  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this study is to determine the role of vascular endothelial function in heart
      failure (HF) and the effect of cardiac resynchronization therapy (CRT) on endothelial and
      cardiac function.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
